title: Marija Spasti Moskvu (2021) Hindi Dubbed
description: Maria Petrova is a young girl who does not want to do what her parents tell her. She is the daughter of a priest, but she is not going to follow in his footsteps. The heroine of the film chooses to serve in the NKVD in order to help people in a different way. Before the battle for Moscow, the girl meets a strange clairvoyant named Matrona. The woman informs Mary that she must deliver the icon of the Mother of God to the capital at all costs. Maria understands that this will be very dangerous, because the icon is behind the front line. The path promises to be difficult and dangerous.
